Mermaid js

```
flowchart TD
    A["push code → aks-lab-app/main"] -->|trigger| B

    subgraph B["Stage Build"]
        B1["docker build & push"]
    end

    B -->|"tag = $(Build.BuildId)"| ACR["ACR"]
    B --> C

    subgraph C["Stage UpdateGitOps"]
        C1["clone gitops repo"]
        C2["yq image.tag = newId"]
        C3["git commit + push"]
        C1 --> C2 --> C3
    end

    C -->|push| GITOPS["aks-lab-gitops/main"]
    GITOPS --> D["ArgoCD auto-sync"]
    D --> E["Pod with new image running"]
```